Package: glasstabs
Title: Animated Glass-Style Tabs and Multi-Select Filter for 'Shiny'
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person("George", "Arthur", , "prigasgenthian48@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for creating animated glassmorphism-style tab
    navigation and multi-select dropdown filters in 'shiny' applications.
    The package provides a tab navigation component and a searchable
    multi-select widget with multiple checkbox indicator styles,
    select-all controls, and customizable colour themes. Additional
    helpers allow tabs to be disabled, badged with numeric counts, rendered
    reactively via 'renderGlassTabs()', and bookmarked via Shiny's URL
    bookmarking system. Built-in example apps can be launched with
    'runGlassExample()'. The widgets are compatible with standard 'shiny'
    layouts and 'bs4Dash' dashboards.
